Slayer ducks under shots from Havoc, gliding in closer to the water. 
He was searching for some sign of Iguanus. The last he'd seen of the 
bot had been over the ocean.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Havoc spinns out of the way of the shots, missing Slayer with several 
of his because of the disturbance. He flies lower to the ocean, 
hopefully making himself a harder target.
